<h1 id="chapter-8-객체-지향의-기초--클래스-안에-포함된-자료형">chapter 8. 객체 지향의 기초 : 클래스 안에 포함된 자료형</h1>

<h2 id="-클래스-내부에서의-중첩-자료형-사용">🔔 클래스 내부에서의 중첩 자료형 사용</h2>

<div class="language-cpp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Fruit</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
<span class="nl">public:</span>
    <span class="k">enum</span> <span class="n">FruitType_1</span>
    <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="n">APPLE</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">BANANA</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">CHERRY</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="p">};</span>

    <span class="k">enum</span> <span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">FruitType_2</span>
    <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="n">APPLE</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">BANANA</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">CHERRY</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="p">};</span>

    <span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">InnerClass</span>
    <span class="p">{</span>
        
    <span class="p">};</span>

    <span class="k">struct</span> <span class="nc">InnerStruct</span>
    <span class="p">{</span>
        
    <span class="p">};</span>

<span class="nl">private:</span>
    <span class="n">FruitType_1</span> <span class="n">type_1</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">FruitType_2</span> <span class="n">type_2</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">InnerClass</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">InnerStruct</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="-클래스-밖에서의-중첩-자료형-사용">🔔 클래스 밖에서의 중첩 자료형 사용</h2>

<div class="language-cpp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="n">Fruit</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">BANANA</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// enum </span>
    <span class="n">Fruit</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">FruitType_2</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">BANANA</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// enum class </span>
    <span class="n">Fruit</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">InnerClass</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// inner-class</span>
    <span class="n">Fruit</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="n">InnerStruct</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="c1">// inner-struct</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

